data.description: A large cozy home on 3.62 mature acres,  Home offers 5 BR, E/I kitchen open to family room. a huge finished basement with wet bar, an enclosed gazebo overlooking backyard, large outdoor entertainment area with firepit, a sperate large work shop with heat and lights, small basketball court, and extra parking for RV or boats.  House was built with in-law suite on second floor in mind.
